### Register
POST /api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

### Login
POST /api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

### Lấy danh sách phim
GET /api/movies?status=NOW_SHOWING&page=1&limit=10

### Lấy chi tiết phim
GET /api/movies/{movieId}

### Admin thêm phim
POST /api/admin/movies
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

### 27. Showtime / Seat / Booking / Payment API từ P6
GET /api/showtimes
GET /api/showtimes/{showtimeId}
GET /api/showtimes/{showtimeId}/seats
POST /api/showtimes/{showtimeId}/holds
DELETE /api/showtimes/{showtimeId}/holds/{showtimeSeatId}
POST /api/bookings
GET /api/bookings/{orderCode}
GET /api/me/bookings
POST /api/payments/mock
GET /api/payments/{paymentCode}
GET /api/bookings/{orderCode}/tickets
